snippet.textDisplay: This is a improvised form of original Sambalpuri  song RANGABATI sung by Jeetendriya Haripal and Krishna Patel. Western Odisha has a different language and culture of it's own.  'SAMBALPURI ' language is different. It's not a dialect of Odiya language.  Sambalpur is famous for ' Sambalpuri ' handloom fabric made by Tie and Dye procedure. The longest earthen Dam of the world is located at Sambalpur  'Hirakud Dam' built across the river Mahanadi.
snippet.textOriginal: This is a improvised form of original Sambalpuri  song RANGABATI sung by Jeetendriya Haripal and Krishna Patel. Western Odisha has a different language and culture of it's own.  'SAMBALPURI ' language is different. It's not a dialect of Odiya language.  Sambalpur is famous for ' Sambalpuri ' handloom fabric made by Tie and Dye procedure. The longest earthen Dam of the world is located at Sambalpur  'Hirakud Dam' built across the river Mahanadi.
